The paper deals with graph theory and combinatorics, specifically the enumeration of perfect matchings in bipartite graphs. This falls under the scope of discrete mathematics (cs.DM), computational complexity (cs.CC), and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also introduces a graph theoretic structure called MinSet Sequence, which is related to computational geometry (cs.CG) and graph theory (cs.GT).
